<plot>In an alternate world, two men work and live in a slave factory. They only know themselves as Presser and Cutter, and their whole life consists of a dingy factory room. They are two of many tools used by a machine, a machine that they are completely dependant on. When the opportunity to escape presents itself, the duo must battle their fears of the outside world. Before they can escape, they must be willing to step into the unknown.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?646617</url></doc>
